title: ProForm Endurance 920 E Elliptical
description: With the Endurance 920 E, you have complete control from the second you step onto the adjustable pedals to the moment you review your stats at the end of a great workout. Get the workout you want with our power ramp. Choose between 24 resistance levels from easy to intense for absolute control. Access all your fitness tools from the 7-inch touchscreen console. Interactive iFit® technology comes built in. That means unlimited workouts that download to your elliptical, Google Maps™ routes anywhere in the world, and instant tracking so you can watch your progress.
